window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><i>The Odyssey</i> is literature's grandest evocation of every man's journey through life. In the myths and legends that are retold here, the energy and poetry of Homer's original is captured in a bold, contemporary idiom, giving us an edition of <i>The Odyssey </i>that is a joy to listen to, worth savoring and treasuring for its sheer lyrical mastery.&nbsp;</p> <p>This audiobook is sure to delight both the classicist and the general listener and to captivate a new generation of Homer's students.&nbsp;</p>"; 
